background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>하지만 많은 회사들이 실패를 하거나 만족스럽지 못한 결과물을 받아들이고 있습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-24759765-f914-4dcd-a880-6d038612eaac\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a0876ad6-8d5c-44b5-ba2b-351ce556ca0c\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>오늘은 인쇄 관련 홈페이지 구축 시 반드시 알아야 할 몇 가지를 적어 봅니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e505f356-c7c5-411c-9f78-976392c51d62\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-e505f356-c7c5-411c-9f78-976392c51d62\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNDA2MTdfMjU4/MDAxNzE4NjAzMzMzMDI5.BZLh8pcIexLY9CQTflCyVBoeKXNn_7SELL6nyEBMvDgg.s6GXyfDegjc1W0sK1DH5SDexVtgqC3kiTXd3lfZAdh4g.PNG/00_%ED%85%9C%ED%94%8C%EB%A6%BF.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"2481\", \"originalHeight\" : \"2599\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNDA2MTdfMjU4/MDAxNzE4NjAzMzMzMDI5.BZLh8pcIexLY9CQTflCyVBoeKXNn_7SELL6nyEBMvDgg.s6GXyfDegjc1W0sK1DH5SDexVtgqC3kiTXd3lfZAdh4g.PNG/00_%ED%85%9C%ED%94%8C%EB%A6%BF.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0a30d400-88c3-4032-bde6-65cfe14bd938\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9930aea8-87d0-4fc